My name is Chris Vincent. Lets start off by just saying that I dont like to follow the crowd, and would rather be my own random self. Youll probably be able to see this within my writings on this website. As is obvious I also like to write. Not just blogging, but short stories, poetry that doesnt really sound like poetry and music. Sport is another activity I enjoy thoroughly (soccer, squash and bicycle riding are my favs :D ). By living in Brisbane, Australia I get to have many opportunities to participate in many communities that like what I like, which is always fun.

Love me, or even try to get annoyed at me, through what Im going to be writing, your going to find something different about me. I dont really like to follow blogging rules, such as sticking with one strict topic, and Im going to attempt to generate some humor in what I write it may not be funny to you, but Ill be having a ball writing it.

Now that you know at least what It seems I like in a real life (yes, its true, theres another perfect world away from this screen. all you have to do is tilt and turn your head to the left), why not sit back, grab some pop-corn, coke, a few chocolates, throw one chocolate to me, and start reading through my interesting blog posts.

I hope you have a lovely day
